how_tiers_work_desc:
Players have one of the 5 levels. The levels change when a certain number of comp points is reached:

No Level (0 - 499 points).
Talent Level (500 - 2999 points). The total amount of deposits to reach the level is 2% of the required bets sum. Player will get 100 free spins (50х2), wager x35.
First 50 free spins will be added immediately, and then you will get 50 spins the next day.
Champion Level (3000 - 9999 points). The total amount of deposits to reach the level is 2% of the required bets sum. Player will get 50 EUR, wager x30.

Star Level (10000 - 49999 points). The total amount of deposits to reach the level is 2% of the required bets sum. Player will get 150 EUR, wager x25.
Legend Level (50000 - 99999 points). The total amount of deposits to reach the level is 1% of the required bets sum. Player will get 300 EUR and 100 free spins
(50x2), wager x20. First 50 free spins will be added immediately, and then you will get 50 spins the next day.

Top Level (100000+ points). The total amount of deposits to reach the level is 1% of the required bets sum. Player will get 500 EUR and 150 free spins (75x2),
wager x15. First 75 free spins will be added immediately, and then you will get 75 spins the next day.
The casino has the right to reset comp points from players who have not been active for the previous 6 months.

Bonus duration is 14 days.

Free spins activation duration is 14 days, free spins duration and free spins result duration are 14 days.

Free spins are awarded as follows:
Talent Level: Striking Joker, Caligula (GameArt) at bet 0.10 EUR
Legend Level: Gates of Olympus, Sugar Rush, Big Bass Bonanza, Madame Destiny Megaways, Wolf Gold (Pragmatic Play).
Top Level: Gates of Olympus, Sugar Rush, Big Bass Bonanza, Madame Destiny Megaways, Wolf Gold (Pragmatic Play).
points_collection_desc:
For every bet placed the player collects two types of points at the same time - status points and redeemable points:

For every 5 EUR real money bets made in slot games the player earns 1 status point.
For every 50 EUR real money bets made in other games the player earns 1 status point.
For every 5 EUR real money bets made in slot games the player earns 1 redeemable point.
For every 150 EUR real money bets made in other games the player earns 1 redeemable point.
Bets made with an active bonus do not contribute to point collection.

how_to_start_desc:
1. Market Research: Conduct extensive market research to understand the target audience, their preferences, and the competitive landscape. Identify what special features or bonuses would appeal to your potential users.

2. Concept Development: Based on your research, define the concept of your casino app, including the types of special bonuses you plan to offer. Brainstorm innovative ideas to make your app stand out in the crowded market.

3. Design and Development: Hire a team of experienced app developers and designers to bring your concept to life. Focus on creating a user-friendly interface, seamless navigation, and visually appealing graphics to enhance the user experience.

4. Bonus System Integration: Implement a robust bonus system that rewards users for their engagement and loyalty. Consider offering welcome bonuses, in-app rewards, VIP bonuses, and other special promotions to keep players engaged.

5. Testing and QA: Before launching your app, conduct thorough testing to identify and fix any bugs or issues. Perform quality assurance checks to ensure that the app functions smoothly across different devices and platforms.
